<div class="container_16 clearfix">
  <div class="grid_18 prefix_4 suffix_4 aligncenter">
    <% if current_user.nil? %>
      <h1>Thank you for signing up!</h1>
      <h3>
        Your payment succeeded and an invitation with further instructions has been
        sent to your email address.
      </h3>
      <p class="small grey">
        Your subscription is linked to the email address you entered on the
        PayPal payment page. Before you can start using your account we need to
        confirm your email address. We have sent you an email with a link.
        Click on the link in the email and everything will be A-OK.
      </p>
      <p class="small grey">
        If you do not receive the email within an hour, contact us at 
        <%= mail_to('support@bitspace.se') %> and we will help you.
        Make sure to check your spam folder as well.
      </p>
    <% else %>
      <h1>Thank you for upgrading!</h1>
      <h3>
        Your payment succeeded and your account will be upgraded
        as soon as we get a notification of the transaction from PayPal, which
        should only take a minute or two.
      </h3>
      <p class="small grey">
        If your account is not automatically upgraded within an hour, please
        contact us at <%= mail_to('support@bitspace.se') %> and we will try
        to help you.
      </p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>